At the age of 25, Our Thais believes call 'Benjaphet' a crucial age that we will met the serious incident or bad lucks in our life.

Currently, I just went through those incidents. It was not that easy for me to overcome those incidents. I just realized that Love and Support from family and friends that I received, is so important in my life to get through this year.
